basic.Peptide Name: CK11 (cytokine, CC family; kinocidins; UCSS1a; 2S=S, natural AMPs; teleost fish, animals; BBMm)
basic.Target Organism: Active against the fish Gram+ pathogen L. garvieae CF00021 (IC50 0.0272 uM), and also  Gram- fish pathogens A. salmonicida subsp. salmonicida (IC50 0.0033 uM) and Y. ruckeri LMG3279 (IC50 0.1407 uM).
